    ⚡ HOW THE PROGRAM WORKS:
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    
    🔹 CORE TECHNOLOGY
    HorribleSubs Downloader operates by connecting to anime release RSS feeds and torrent sources. The program continuously monitors these feeds for new episodes of your subscribed series, automatically fetching torrent files or magnet links and initiating downloads through your preferred torrent client. It intelligently organizes downloaded content into series folders with proper naming conventions .
    
    🔹 DOWNLOAD PROCESS
    The software follows a streamlined workflow:
    
    • RSS MONITORING: Connects to HorribleSubs/subsplease RSS feeds
    • SERIES TRACKING: Monitors for new episodes of your followed shows
    • QUALITY SELECTION: Filters releases based on resolution (1080p, 720p, 480p)
    • TORRENT HANDLING: Downloads torrent files or generates magnet links
    • CLIENT INTEGRATION: Sends downloads to uTorrent, qBittorrent, or other clients
    • AUTOMATIC ORGANIZATION: Moves completed files to structured folders
    
    🔹 RSS FEED INTEGRATION
    The program supports multiple RSS feed sources:
    
    • SUBSPLEASE FEED: Primary source for anime releases
    • HORRIBLESUBS ARCHIVE: Access to historical releases
    • CUSTOM FEEDS: Add any anime release RSS feed
    • FILTERED FEEDS: Create custom feeds by quality or fansub group
    
    🔹 SERIES MANAGEMENT
    
    • SUBSCRIPTIONS: Follow specific series for automatic downloads
    • WATCHLIST: Track which episodes you've already downloaded
    • SEASON TRACKING: Automatically detect and follow new seasons
    • COMPLETED SERIES: Mark series as complete and stop monitoring
    • FAVORITES: Quick access to your most-watched shows
    
    🔹 QUALITY SELECTION
    Choose your preferred release quality:
    
    • 1080p FULL HD: Highest quality, larger file sizes
    • 720p HD: Balanced quality and file size
    • 480p SD: Smaller files, lower quality
    • BEST AVAILABLE: Auto-selects highest quality present
    • CUSTOM: Set quality preferences per series
    
    🔹 TORRENT CLIENT SUPPORT
    Integrates with popular torrent clients:
    
    • qBITTORRENT: Native integration with WebUI and local client
    • uTORRENT: Support for both classic and WebUI versions
    • DELUGE: Integration via WebAPI
    • TRANSMISSION: Support for remote Transmission instances
    • MAGNET LINKS: Direct magnet link handling
    • TORRENT FILES: Automatic torrent file downloading
    
    🔹 AUTOMATION FEATURES
    
    • SCHEDULED CHECKS: Automatically check for new episodes at set intervals
    • INSTANT NOTIFICATION: Real-time download when new episodes release
    • BACKFILL DOWNLOAD: Download missing episodes from previous seasons
    • COMPLETE SERIES: One-click download of entire series
    • WEEKLY SCHEDULE: View and download based on release schedules
    
    🔹 ORGANIZATION
    Automatically organizes your anime collection:
    
    • SERIES FOLDERS: Creates folders for each anime series
    • SEASON FOLDERS: Organizes episodes by season number
    • NAMING CONVENTION: Consistent episode naming (Series - S01E01 - Title)
    • METADATA: Optional metadata tagging for media servers
    • DUPLICATE DETECTION: Skips already downloaded episodes
    
    🔹 USER INTERFACE
    
    • SERIES BROWSER: Browse available series with cover art
    • RELEASE CALENDAR: View upcoming releases by date
    • DOWNLOAD QUEUE: Monitor active and pending downloads
    • SEARCH FUNCTION: Find specific series quickly
    • FILTER OPTIONS: Filter by genre, season, or popularity
    • DARK MODE: Easy on the eyes for nighttime use
    
    🔹 ADVANCED FEATURES
    
    • KEYWORD FILTERING: Exclude releases with specific keywords
    • FANSUB PREFERENCE: Prioritize specific fansub groups
    • LANGUAGE SELECTION: Choose subtitle languages
    • POST-PROCESSING: Run scripts after download completion
    • RSS FILTERS: Advanced filtering using regex patterns
    • NOTIFICATIONS: Desktop and email alerts for new downloads
    
    🔹 MEDIA SERVER INTEGRATION
    Works seamlessly with media server software:
    
    • PLEX: Automatic library scanning after downloads
    • JELLYFIN: Trigger library updates on new content
    • EMBY: Post-download organization for Emby servers
    • KODI: Library update notifications
    
    🔹 DOWNLOAD STATISTICS
    
    • DOWNLOAD HISTORY: Complete log of all downloads
    • BANDWIDTH USAGE: Track monthly download totals
    • SERIES STATISTICS: How many episodes per series downloaded
    • COMPLETION RATES: Track your watching progress
    
